reviewText: This guy is great. Hope he continues to expose  Jimi's music to the uninitiated. Great chops.
this guitar player is OFF THE CHARTS !!!!!!!!!!!!  AWESOME !!!!!!!!!!!!!!
If you like Jimi Hendrix you will like this. I just wished it had some of my favorites on it.
Randy Hansen is an incredible musician and Hendrix Tribute artist. This DVD is a witness to the fact, that Randy really keeps the Jimi spirt flame alight!
